name: ranResource
description: A RAN resource (cell, Wi-Fi access point, or backhaul link)

resourceSpecification.name: ranResourceSpec
resourceSpecification.description: This resourceSpecification describes a cell/access point/backhaul link.

resourceSpecCharacteristic.name: ranType
resourceSpecCharacteristic.description: The type of RAN resource. The possible values can be cell, access point or backhaul link.

resourceSpecCharacteristic.name: geographicalLocation
resourceSpecCharacteristic.description: The geographical coordinates the RAN resource is physically installed.

resourceSpecCharacteristic.name: technology
resourceSpecCharacteristic.description: The wireless tecnology of the RAN resource.

resourceSpecCharacteristic.name: operationBand
resourceSpecCharacteristic.description: Lists the available Wi-Fi channels or 3GPP operation bands.

resourceSpecCharacteristic.name: minDlFrequency
resourceSpecCharacteristic.description: The minimum Downlink frequency (MHz) that can be used for each operationBand.

resourceSpecCharacteristic.name: maxDlFrequency
resourceSpecCharacteristic.description: The maximum Downlink frequency (MHz) that can be used for each operationBand.

resourceSpecCharacteristic.name: minUlFrequency
resourceSpecCharacteristic.description: The minimum Uplink frequency (MHz) that can be used for each operationBand.

resourceSpecCharacteristic.name: maxUlFrequency
resourceSpecCharacteristic.description: The maximum Downlink frequency (MHz) that can be used for each operationBand.

resourceSpecCharacteristic.name: bandwidth
resourceSpecCharacteristic.description: Lists the supported system bandwidths of each operationBand.

resourceSpecCharacteristic.name: txPower
resourceSpecCharacteristic.description: The maximum transmission power.

resourceSpecCharacteristic.name: quota
resourceSpecCharacteristic.description: The maximum percentage of the total resources available.
